pull.title: Add TheCharlatan's pgp key
pull.body: Since I have submitted my pair of signed gitian assertions, I am now adding my key's fingerprint to the gitian keys list.

Add TheCharlatan's pgp key

events.body: Generally we add keys after signing for two major releases. I see that [you've committed](https://github.com/bitcoin-core/gitian.sigs/commits?author=TheCharlatan) unsigned sigs for 0.18.1 and 0.19.0. Are you planning on producing the signed sigs as well?
Yes, I'll contribute them once the 0.19.0.0 detached sigs are up.

issue.title: Bitcoin PR tracking
issue.body: The main purpose of this issue is to keep track of Pull Requests on Bitcoin since version 0.19.1 identifying those which make a porting LitecoinZ.
